-- Kharafi Seeks to Bring Pinewood Studios to Egypt, National Says
-- B y   A y e s h a   D a y a
-- 2012-05-11T05:28:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-11/kharafi-seeks-to-bring-pinewood-studios-to-egypt-national-says.html
Kuwait’s  Kharafi Group  is in talks to
bring Pinewood Studios, a U.K. film and television company, to
 Egypt , where Kharafi is building a Red Sea tourism resort, the
National reported, citing Adel Rady, who heads Kharafi’s Marsa
Alam Tourism Development unit.  Talks that began two years ago and were postponed during
Egypt’s revolution are being revived and Kharafi is seeking to
establish a free zone for Pinewood, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ayesha Daya in Dubai 
 adaya1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
